data.description: Nestled in the HEART of Trussville! ONLY 5 minutes to the entertainment district! This three bedroom home with a FINISHED basement is ready for it's new owners. You'll notice the large wrap-around front porch, offering a warm welcome and a perfect spot for enjoying the Southern breeze. Upon entering, you're greeted with hardwood floors in the spacious living room and dining room. Beat the cold with your warm cozy fireplace. The kitchen has stainless steel appliances and plenty of room. Another favorite feature is the large sunroom, which is currently being used for a home office and craft room. The primary bedroom is on the main level and the other bedrooms are upstairs. The finished basement is perfect for a play room or a second living area. Lastly, this CORNER lot is huge and offers a fenced -in backyard with a screened in patio and large deck. Bring all your backyard parties here! Schedule your private showing TODAY!
